  "title": "HR Support Intern/ Temp",
  "description": "<p>Kickstart your career in recruitment and experience how tech meets talent through <strong>Octomate Staffing</strong>! Be part of a team that connects amazing candidates to the right roles and helps companies grow. 🌟</p><p>📍: Orchard</p><p>🕗: 8:30am - 5:30pm, Monday - Friday</p><p>📆: At least 3 months</p><p><strong>💼 Your Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Create, post and manage job advertisements</li><li>Shortlist top talents for different roles</li><li>Conduct interviews and coordinate offers with different stakeholders </li></ul><p><strong>✅ Who we are looking for</strong></p><ul><li>Confident and upbeat</li><li>Highly organised and eager to learn in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Can commit for at least 3 months</li><li>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma / Degree (any field)</li></ul><p><strong>✨Why you will love it</strong></p><ul><li>Hands-on exposure to the world of recruitment</li><li>Real opportunity to learn, grow, and possibly extend or convert</li></ul>",
